{"tid":404164,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[又嚟] Google Play Store 被駭客入侵（多達2000萬人中伏）","createTime":"2017-09-17T23:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T06:51:50.000Z","uid":1886,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"655a372add34da27436a6ea708bbb4ccc421c4b1","tid":404164,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:27:29.000Z","msg":"智能手機作業系統Android爆發大規模黑客事件，黑客透過在Google Play Store（圖）的應用程式植入惡意軟件「ExpensiveWall」，盜竊用戶金錢，受害者可能多達2,110萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170916/large/chris99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170916%2Flarge%2Fchris99.jpg&h=deb71b9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170916/20154373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170916%2F20154373&d=dfVp40sK0uRlKjoKzgMyZTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=7b151b11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170916%2F20154373&h=96e2bf82\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170916/20154373</a></div><br />\n<br />\n事件由以色列網絡保安公司Check Point揭發，黑客將惡意程式加密避過Google過濾，入侵至少50個應用程式，下載次數或多達400萬次。加上早前防毒軟件公司McAfee發現同類病毒的另一版本，估計受害用戶人數介乎590萬至2,110萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。中招的手機會發出詐騙性收費短訊，令用戶收到天價電話賬單。手機威脅研究員帕登表示：「就規模病毒效果而言，這是入侵Google Play Store的其中一次牽連最廣的惡意軟件浪潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」<br />\n<br />\nCheck Point上月7日向Google通知事件，涉事應用程式隨即被下架。但黑客很快重施故技，再次發佈病毒另一變種，4日內入侵至少5,000部手機。Google發言人表示現已處理了被入侵的應用程式，並感謝科技界努力確保Android生態系統安全。<br />\n<br />\n美國《福布斯》/《財富》"},{"pid":"e65bd7cac14a39d248f620baf099bad728bcf8bf","tid":404164,"uid":63,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2b798b81cc028ea7b8a0f21c3b6f1df9ced965","tid":404164,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:31:52.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕Google Play商店被發現約50款藏有惡意程式的APP，受害者多達2110萬人，被形容為目前針對安卓軟體最大宗的攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報導，網路安全公司Check Point在14日向Google提出警告，Google Play商店中有大量藏有名為ExpensiveWall惡意程式的APP，駭客將惡意程式包裝在包有大量免費桌布、相機與照片編輯的APP中，至少有50款藏有相同惡意程式的APP曾於Google Play上架，且可能有更多樣的偽裝手法。在今年初，類似惡意程式的程式碼也被McAfee偵測到，主要藏於相機和照片編輯APP中。<br />\n<br />\n資安專家說明，惡意軟體會在受害者不知情的狀況下傳送高額簡訊、訂閱使用偽造的昂貴服務，向受害者索取費用。而ExpensiveWall特別之處在於，駭客設計讓它<span style=\"color: red;\">能躲過Google Play中內建的反惡意程式保護</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n目前Google已將感染惡意程式的APP下架，但Check Point公司指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">此惡意程式容易被修改，未來會以其它型態出現</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2195176\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2195176&d=dfVp40sK0uRlKjoKzgMyZTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f30ee79a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2195176&h=f5928ac4\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2195176</a>"},{"pid":"d2bca8995257766f718e7677879f6b350eef4ec7","tid":404164,"uid":17103,"like":8,"dislike":26,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:34:15.000Z","msg":"App Store 都有啦, Google 有 Big Data Machine Learning 唔似蘋果根本就唔入流. 重有你可以用 Amazon 或者自己 Download App. <br />\n<br />\n垃圾 idog 隨時係敵方比錢人 hack 入 Google Play Store. 不招人妒時庸才."},{"pid":"6b2b876a10584002b60aa2443f251496ca210988","tid":404164,"uid":144497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:47:33.000Z","msg":"相片與照片編輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abcc821d8372267710e900affbc29f32c40b629","tid":404164,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:52:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>App Store 都有啦, Google 有 Big Data Machine Learning 唔似蘋果根本就唔入流. 重有你可以用 Amazon 或者自己 Download App. <br />\n<br />\n垃圾 idog 隨時係敵方比錢人 hack 入 Google Play Store. 不招人妒時庸才.</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48bf9dfc318b03b2ebf1f7061cfa6eebf53cb8ba","tid":404164,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:08:35.000Z","msg":"「好人好姐黑客點會攪你？」<br />\n「有防毒apps唔怕」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n惡意軟體會在受害者不知情的狀況下傳送高額簡訊、訂閱使用偽造的昂貴服務，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0634680a458e87d5859dabe04e4913c9771b85e2","tid":404164,"uid":10788,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:11:07.000Z","msg":"不招人妒時庸才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿Sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我被人入屋打劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黑警：不招人妒時庸才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e5ca4525f1eb6360ad69024b259641ff9a8959e","tid":404164,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:12:47.000Z","msg":"正評上一頁"},{"pid":"ec18a13c4424099f21f9fc8565648aea5d8adde7","tid":404164,"uid":49,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:13:53.000Z","msg":"比人偷錢偷到傻撚左"},{"pid":"da368e94d028d6ad0ac50e8424735e0e85947be1","tid":404164,"uid":25858,"lik